title: Ohio State basketball does not receive an invitation to the NIT
text: COLUMBUS, Ohio -- Thad Matta said after Ohio State basketball was bounced from the Big Ten Tournament by Rutgers that he wasn't sure if the Buckeyes would accept a bid to the National Invitation Tournament. Turns out he didn't need...
